data.description: Remodeled doll house in the Willow Glen of Gilroy! Primary bedroom featuring walkin closet, new primary bath, all new fixtures, spacious walkin tiled shower, dual vanities w/ sink! Hall bath has been enlarged & redone, new tub w/ tiled shower over, new vanity, all new fixtures. Family room now open to remodeled kitchen! Fresh paint inside & outside, new luxury vinyl & new carpet. all new appliances, gas stove, new refrigerator, island w/ sink, white kit cabinets, new canned lights thru out the house, interior laundry room. Detached ADU redone! 12X24 features new bathroom, new kitchenette, fresh paint, new flooring!! Detached two car garage off alley. Plenty of room to add another ADU!  Long driveway at side of house, spacious fenced backyard, dual pane windows, new front & rear doors. Homes don't come up for sale very often in this neighborhood!!  You'll love calling this home and love coming home!!
